reviewText: This is a good dvd to start out on.  Easy to follow and fun.  Can't wait to try the other ones.
This is a great workout video, but do wish it was little longer. It is easy to follow along with the instructor, she makes it fun and easy to use.  Doesn't feel like your working out.
The video quality is professional, the music gets you moving, and the instructor's explanations are easy to understand. The dances really target the abs & are fun to learn.
Very happy with this workout - great for an add-on or a light day workout. Very effective for abs and legs too!
This DVD was too short.  I don't think you can work your abs and legs in just 20 minutes.  I just wish this DVD was longer, and more routines were included.
